@startuml hub_spoke_bedrock

title Hub-and-Spoke Multi-Agent Architecture\nAWS Bedrock (ap-southeast-1) — Claude Sonnet 4.6

skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam defaultFontColor #1e1e2e
skinparam defaultFontName Monospaced
skinparam ArrowColor #1e66f5
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor #9ca0b0

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #eff1f5
    BorderColor #9ca0b0
    FontColor #1e1e2e
}

skinparam database {
    BackgroundColor #dce0e8
    BorderColor #9ca0b0
    FontColor #1e1e2e
}

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #e6e9ef
    BorderColor #9ca0b0
    FontColor #4c4f69
}

actor       User            as U        #89dceb
participant "Hub\n(Coordinator)"        as HUB      #cba6f7
participant "Spoke 1\nWeb Researcher"   as WEB      #a6e3a1
participant "Spoke 2\nDoc Analyzer"     as DOC      #fab387
participant "Spoke 3\nSynthesizer"      as SYN      #f9e2af
participant "Spoke 4\nReport Writer"    as RPT      #89b4fa
database    "ResearchState\n(Pydantic)" as STATE    #585b70
participant "Bedrock\nConverse API"     as BEDROCK  #f38ba8

== Stage 1: Goal Decomposition ==

U -> HUB : goal (string)
HUB -> BEDROCK : converse(HUB_PROMPT, goal)
BEDROCK --> HUB : JSON list of subtasks\n[{agent, task}, ...]
HUB -> STATE : store subtasks\n(local Python list)
note right of HUB
  stop_reason: end_turn
  No tools used
end note

== Stage 2: Discovery Spokes ==

HUB -> WEB : subtask {agent: WebResearcher, task}
WEB -> BEDROCK : converse(WEB_RESEARCHER_PROMPT,\ntask, toolConfig)
BEDROCK --> WEB : stop_reason: tool_use\n[simulate_web_search(query)]
WEB -> WEB : execute simulate_web_search()
WEB -> BEDROCK : converse(..., tool_result)
BEDROCK --> WEB : stop_reason: end_turn\nraw text findings
WEB -> STATE : state.raw_web.append(result)

HUB -> DOC : subtask {agent: DocAnalyzer, task}
DOC -> BEDROCK : converse(DOC_ANALYZER_PROMPT,\ntask, toolConfig)
BEDROCK --> DOC : stop_reason: tool_use\n[extract_document_data(topic)]
DOC -> DOC : execute extract_document_data()
DOC -> BEDROCK : converse(..., tool_result)
BEDROCK --> DOC : stop_reason: end_turn\nraw extracted data
DOC -> STATE : state.raw_doc.append(result)

== Stage 3: Synthesis (Hard Wall) ==

STATE -> SYN : state.raw_web + state.raw_doc\n(concatenated strings)
SYN -> BEDROCK : converse(SYNTHESIZER_PROMPT,\nraw combined data)\nno tools
BEDROCK --> SYN : JSON only — FactBase schema\n(no prose, no markdown)
SYN -> SYN : FactBase.model_validate_json()\nPydantic validation
note right of SYN
  ⛔ ValidationError raised here
  if JSON is malformed —
  pipeline halts immediately
end note
SYN -> STATE : state.fact_base = fact_base.model_dump()

== Stage 4: Report Generation ==

STATE -> RPT : state.fact_base (dict → JSON string)\nNO raw data passed
RPT -> BEDROCK : converse(REPORT_WRITER_PROMPT,\nfact_base_json)\nno tools
BEDROCK --> RPT : Markdown executive report\n(only facts from Fact Base)
RPT -> STATE : state.final_report = markdown

== Output ==

STATE -> U : state.final_report\n(rich Markdown render)
STATE -> U : state.fact_base\n(rich Panel JSON inspect)

note over STATE
  ResearchState is the ONLY communication channel.
  Agents never call each other directly.
  Each stage receives an immutable copy via model_copy().
end note

@enduml
